description: Enforce alias-based absolute imports across src
globs: src/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: true
---

# Absolute Imports Only

- Use alias-based absolute imports for all in-repo modules under `src`.
- Required alias format: `@/path/to/module`.
- Do not use relative imports such as `./` or `../` in `src` code.
- Keep third-party imports unchanged (for example `react`, `tldraw`).

Examples:

```ts
// bad
import { useModelConversion } from "../hooks/use-model-conversion"

// good
import { useModelConversion } from "@/domains/model-conversion/hooks/use-model-conversion"
```
